    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop the <strong>sweet potato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> (skins on) into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
